abstract: The Baltimore Ravens wrapped American Football Conference's (AFC) top seed and home field advantage for the NFL playoffs by beating the Cleveland Browns 31-15 on Sunday but it will take out another week to sort out the National Football Conference (NFC).
snippet: The Baltimore Ravens wrapped American Football Conference's (AFC) top seed and home field advantage for the NFL playoffs by beating the Cleveland Browns 31-15 on Sunday but it will take out another week to sort out the National Football Conference...
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - The Baltimore Ravens wrapped American Football Conference's (AFC) top seed and home field advantage for the NFL playoffs by beating the Cleveland Browns 31-15 on Sunday but it will take out another week to sort out the National Football Conference (NFC).
headline_main: Ravens Grab AFC Top Seed, but NFC Up for Grabs
headline_print_headline: Ravens Grab AFC Top Seed, but NFC Up for Grabs

abstract: At least 11 people have been killed and more than 300 treated in hospital after drinking coconut wine in the Philippines, including some who were celebrating at a Christmas party, health and local authorities said on Monday.
snippet: At least 11 people have been killed and more than 300 treated in hospital after drinking coconut wine in the Philippines, including some who were celebrating at a Christmas party, health and local authorities said on Monday.
lead_paragraph: MANILA — At least 11 people have been killed and more than 300 treated in hospital after drinking coconut wine in the Philippines, including some who were celebrating at a Christmas party, health and local authorities said on Monday.
headline_main: Eleven Dead, 300 Treated After Drinking Coconut Wine in Philippines
headline_print_headline: Eleven Dead, 300 Treated After Drinking Coconut Wine in Philippines

abstract: South Korean exports fell again in the first 20 days of December, but a recovery in demand from China and stabilising chip prices offered signs that a year-long run of declines may be nearing its end.
snippet: South Korean exports fell again in the first 20 days of December, but a recovery in demand from China and stabilising chip prices offered signs that a year-long run of declines may be nearing its end.
lead_paragraph: SEOUL — South Korean exports fell again in the first 20 days of December, but a recovery in demand from China and stabilising chip prices offered signs that a year-long run of declines may be nearing its end.
headline_main: South Korea 20-Day Exports Fall, but China Demand Offers Hope
headline_print_headline: South Korea 20-Day Exports Fall, but China Demand Offers Hope

abstract: Philadelphia took control of the N.F.C. East and turned up the pressure on Dallas Coach Jason Garrett.
snippet: Philadelphia took control of the N.F.C. East and turned up the pressure on Dallas Coach Jason Garrett.
lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA — The Dallas Cowboys like to call themselves America’s Team, but these days they could also star on an episode of “The Apprentice,” with Coach Jason Garrett trying to convince the team owner Jerry Jones that he deserves to keep his job.
